• Specialist consultations
• Prescriptions

• Eye infections (pink eye/conjunctivitis)

• Allergies

• Medical testing
• Specialist consultations
• Prescriptions

• Skin issues (rash, acne, and more)
• Eye infections (pink eye/conjunctivitis)
• Mental health (depression, anxiety, PTSD, and more)
• Chronic care (high blood pressure, high cholesterol, allergies, asthma, acid reflux and more)

• Prescription renewals
• Allergies

• Non-Urgent Paediatric Care
